<section id="about">
<div class="section-container reveal">
<div class="section-label">// about krevaix</div>
<h2 class="section-title">Built by someone who understands<br>operations from the inside</h2>
<div class="about-layout">
<div class="about-text">
<p>KrevAIx was founded on a simple observation: operations-driven businesses waste thousands of hours every year on tasks AI can handle in minutes. Quotes that take days. Reports that eat up evenings. Permits filled out by hand for the hundredth time.</p>
<p>We don't build generic automation from templates. We come from the field services world — we understand 12-hour days, crews spread across the country, and the pressure to get things right the first time.</p>
<p>Every system we build is designed for how your business actually operates, not how a software company thinks it should.</p>
</div>
<div class="about-highlights">
<div class="about-highlight"><div class="about-highlight-icon">&#127919;</div><div><h4>Operations-First Approach</h4><p>We study your actual workflows before building anything. No cookie-cutter solutions.</p></div></div>
<div class="about-highlight"><div class="about-highlight-icon">&#128295;</div><div><h4>Custom-Built Systems</h4><p>Every automation is tailored to your specific processes, tools, and team.</p></div></div>
<div class="about-highlight"><div class="about-highlight-icon">&#128640;</div><div><h4>Ongoing Partnership</h4><p>We don't build and disappear. Your systems get maintained and evolved over time.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
